99-0104 (La. 4/23/99)

Rhonda Renee HOLT, et al. v. CANNON EXPRESS CORPORATION, et al. No. 99-C-0104. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Cannon Express Corp. Et Al; Vanliner Insurance Co.; Ramsey, Bobby; — Defendant(s); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Parish of Caddo First Judicial District Court Div. “I” Number 385,151; to the Court of Appeal, Second Circuit, Number 31271-CA

Denied.

MARCUS and TRAYLOR, JJ. would grant the writ. VICTORY, J. not on panel.
